snippet.title: Untamed Isles | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
It's almost time to explore the Untamed Isles!

This unique turn-based MMO offers a stunning 3D socially driven world, with an unmatched number of unique monsters to encounter, tame, battle, and breed.

Explore, make friends, and chase fame and fortune in the Untamed Isles.

More information to be found in the coming weeks through our Discord and upcoming Kickstarter.

Join us on Discord to get involved and keep updated!

Untamed Isles Website: https://untamedisles.com/
Untamed Isles Discord: https://discord.gg/untamedislesofficial
Untamed Isles on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1823300/Untamed_Isles/

#untamedisles #gaming #monstertaming
